oc:kn_0516562b a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When deciding between minimal vs full plugin structure" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use the minimal plugin pattern for quick prototypes, single-purpose utilities, learning plugin development, or internal team tools with one specific function." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Over-engineering a plugin with unnecessary directories and config slows development for simple use cases." .

oc:kn_0a7c7d0f a oc:CodePattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When scaffolding a new plugin" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Directory structure: hello-world/ → .claude-plugin/plugin.json + commands/hello.md. Command files use YAML frontmatter with 'name' and 'description' fields, followed by markdown instructions." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Claude Code auto-discovers commands by scanning the commands/ directory for .md files with frontmatter." .

oc:kn_1b35a5be a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When writing plugin.json" ;
    oc:directiveContent "The plugin.json manifest must contain at minimum the 'name' field. Other fields (version, description, author) are optional enhancements." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Claude Code requires the name field to identify and register the plugin; without it, discovery fails." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_202f0474 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Procedure ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When building a minimal plugin" ;
    oc:directiveContent "1. Create project directory 2. Add .claude-plugin/plugin.json with name field 3. Create commands/ directory 4. Add .md command files with YAML frontmatter (name, description) and instruction body" ;
    oc:hasRationale "This ordered sequence ensures the plugin is discoverable and functional at each step." ;
    oc:stepOrder 1 .

oc:kn_4b579f42 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When creating a new plugin from scratch" ;
    oc:directiveContent "A minimal plugin requires only a .claude-plugin/plugin.json with a name field and a commands/ directory with at least one .md file. No scripts, hooks, or external resources are needed." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Establishes the absolute minimum viable structure — every additional feature (agents, hooks, metadata) is optional and layered on top." .

oc:kn_f7c474ad a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Procedure ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When growing a minimal plugin into a full-featured one" ;
    oc:directiveContent "To extend: 1. Add more .md files in commands/ 2. Update plugin.json with version, description, author 3. Create agents/ directory for agent definitions 4. Create hooks/hooks.json for event handling" ;
    oc:hasRationale "Provides a clear upgrade path from minimal to production-ready without restructuring." ;
    oc:stepOrder 2 .

